  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-05 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial sample introduces W-CON-05: a VerificationActivity (mesh-independence study) is declared via hasVerificationActivity but no Evidence or ValidationResult in the package emits prov:wasGeneratedBy pointing back to that activity, leaving it an orphan declaration.",
