    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor shortfalls relative to MRL 5 requirements, the assessment team accepted the package for submission on the basis that the identified gaps are documented and a remediation plan is in place. The mesh independence study declared under hasVerificationActivity is noted as a key outstanding item; however, no evidence artifact has been linked to that activity, and its results therefore cannot be credited toward the discretization error factor at this time. Full acceptance of the hemolysis prediction claim is deferred pending evidence linkage.",
